quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,78,"Mu by’ukuri, no muri bo hari abagoreka indimi zabo iyo basoma igitabo (Tawurati), kugira ngo mukeke ko biri mu gitabo, kandi bitari mu gitabo. Bakavuga bati \"Ibyo ni ibyaturutse kwa Allah\"kandi bitaraturutse kwa Allah. Bakanahimbira Allah ikinyoma kandi babizi"
  3,79,"Ntibibaho ko umuntu Allah yahaye igitabo, gukiranura abantu ndetse akanamuha n’ubuhanuzi, maze narangiza abwire abantu ati \"Nimube abagaragu banjye aho kuba aba Allah\". Ahubwo (yababwira ati) \"Nimube abamenyi bubaha Allah kuko mwigishaga igitabo no kubera ko mwakigaga"
  3,80,Ndetse nta n’ubwo yabategeka kugira abamalayika n’abahanuzi ibigirwamana. Ese yabategeka guhakana nyuma Abayisilamu? y’uko mubaye
  3,81,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Allah yahaga abahanuzi isezerano rikomeye (rigira riti) \"Nimbaha igitabo n’ubushishozi, maze Intumwa (Muhamadi) ikabageraho ishimangira ibyo mufite, mugomba kuzayemera mukanayirengera\". Aravuga (Allah) ati \"Ese murabyemeye munabigira isezerano ryanjye?\" Baravuga bati \"Turabyemeye\". Aravuga ati \"Ngaho nimubihamye, nanjye ndi kumwe namwe mu babihamya"
  3,82,"Ariko abazigomeka nyuma y’ibyo, abo ni bo nkozi z’ibibi"
  3,83,"Ese idini ritari irya Allah ni ryo bashaka, kandi ari we ibiri mu birere no mu isi byicishaho bugufi, bibishaka cyangwa bitabishaka? Kandi iwe ni ho bose bazasubizwa"